Add a small dropdown to the resource balance so we can select a specific factory or all factories
	Would be nice to be able to see the resource balance for a specific factory, or all factories combined.
	Dropdown to select factory or "All Factories"
	When "All Factories" is selected, show the total resource balance for all factories combined.
	When a specific factory is selected, show the resource balance for that factory only.
	This allows the tool to be useful when designing a single factory, or when managing multiple factories.
	Should default to "All Factories"


